name: Blackberry Baked Feta
instructions: Preheat the oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C).
Place feta cheese in the center of a small baking dish. Drizzle 1 tablespoon honey over feta cheese. Bake for 10 minutes.
Remove from the oven and top with blackberries. Drizzle with remaining 1/2 tablespoon honey. Bake until cheese is soft, about 10 minutes more. Serve immediately with sliced baguette.
